  "texts": [
    "For simplicity, we associate each paper to its first (and most relevant) field of study.",
    "To create the sequences to analyze, for each field we consider the first 1000 journals in terms of number of English papers.",
    "Then, for each journal, we order the published papers based on the respective year of publication, volume, issue, and first page.",
    "When some of this information is not available, the Semantic Scholar unique ID of the paper is also used in the ordering process.",
    "Thus, for each paper, we extract and lemmatize their title, similarly to what done for the Project Gutenberg."
  ],
